{"tid":2166741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人肉地毯習俗】中國大使踩小童背 外交部：有人故意誣衊抹黑","createTime":"2020-08-20T15:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T15:34:28.000Z","uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"34884d0830ecdbe1aba25d737ca49f0bd0fbbd51","tid":2166741,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"太平洋的島國基里巴斯（Kiribati）去年與台灣斷交後，投入中國大陸的懷抱，但<span class=\"red\">中國駐基里巴斯大使唐松根造訪該國的一個外島時，當他下飛機後毫不猶豫地從「人肉地毯」走過</span>，照片遭國際言論撻伐。澳洲有學者表示這是當地族人迎賓習俗，但基里巴斯前總統的幕僚表示，很多民眾對此感到難過、惡心，更直言台灣大使根本不會這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnhUuYR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnhUuYR.png&h=d72f5df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》則訪問曾擔任基里巴斯前總統湯安諾的幕僚、現為獨立記者的里蒙（Rimon Rimon），他指出，<span class=\"red\">過去還和台灣建交時，台灣大使也曾到過馬拉凱島，但他沒有這樣做</span>，更表示街上很多民眾看到這個情況後，都感到難過且憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/DYL6BUZLQFDGTE4QABRFQVA4FE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FDYL6BUZLQFDGTE4QABRFQVA4FE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5VKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=91766f0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FDYL6BUZLQFDGTE4QABRFQVA4FE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=fcd18fe8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/DYL6BUZLQFDGTE4QABRFQVA4FE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"82851917b36522e6fb06f9ea39ffd130aacba95b","tid":2166741,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1ea12afafae72e4272f2aac2f775bc8b94069333","tid":2166741,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:09:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f5e7065262da99f177aaf93d0f612df46ad455e6","tid":2166741,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:09:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e422c057a56333f62ad0f69be34287f2d482fb85","tid":2166741,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"即係基里巴斯政府奶共，中國大使又欣然接受安排？"},{"pid":"76e48605fb1c8358475c31dc61ff630bf89b9b1b","tid":2166741,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"踩背<br />\n<br />\n醫學交流"},{"pid":"520b377ec9d0fbef184ea2e7de0ca46a3fe4272f","tid":2166741,"uid":158888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"但基里巴斯前總統的幕僚表示，很多民眾對此感到難過、惡心，<span class=\"red\">更直言台灣大使根本不會這樣做</span>。<br />\n<br />\n人同畜牲既分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0435378ad52925bd91e56b9242faea9251e079ee","tid":2166741,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:15:24.000Z","msg":"中式按摩都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444e4420dcdf042da7cfd762aee43c92149f2565","tid":2166741,"uid":78538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:34:28.000Z","msg":"中國大使為基里巴斯小童背部按摩，體現兩國深厚交情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}